org.eclipse.rdf4j.rio

Interface RDFWriterFactory

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    BinaryRDFWriterFactory, JSONLDWriterFactory, N3WriterFactory, NQuadsWriterFactory, NTriplesWriterFactory, RDFJSONWriterFactory, RDFXMLPrettyWriterFactory, RDFXMLWriterFactory, TriGStarWriterFactory, TriGWriterFactory, TriXWriterFactory, TurtleStarWriterFactory, TurtleWriterFactory

    public interface RDFWriterFactory
    A RDFWriterFactory returns RDFWriters for a specific RDF format.
    Author:
    Arjohn Kampman

        RDFWriter getWriter(OutputStream out,
                    String baseURI)
             throws URISyntaxException

        baseURI - The URI associated with the data in the InputStream.
